{"tid":1000980,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"新手租屋一問","createTime":"2019-01-29T21:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T22:05:47.000Z","uid":85098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e1edde64712e91734ab4a56880499392069b3e9e","tid":1000980,"uid":85098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T21:52:06.000Z","msg":"想各位巴打絲打幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我宜家租屋呢度個業主好撚煩，因為我間房係share同其他人住，個屋主成日帶埋d所謂嘅親戚話上黎懷念下佢地間舊屋🖕🏿成日都煩撚住曬！<br />\n今個月打算交租俾佢個陣佢話要加成1000蚊租，本身我都打算4月搬走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家諗唔到計仔點樣拖住佢呢幾個月唔好加租，又唔洗俾佢煩帶埋d唔知乜人上黎睇樓拜神...最尾退租又可以拎翻啲押金走😢<br />\n各位巴打絲打有無意見比到我😭"},{"pid":"4406de36f9fe80b481eb9c00a4825e57ba98c089","tid":1000980,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T22:00:48.000Z","msg":"租樓日日賺架喎 個1000蚊唔係比唔起啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251cef60789d1cda7ccded6feea3d8f0254c25fd","tid":1000980,"uid":85098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4406de36f9fe80b481eb9c00a4825e57ba98c089","tid":1000980,"uid":110988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T22:00:48.000Z","msg":"租樓日日賺架喎 個1000蚊唔係比唔起啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T22:05:47.000Z","msg":"而喺唔想再俾個屋主煩住曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有得搬梗係搬，但都要等到4月"}]}